# 🚀 AI-OppHub — Hackathon, Grant & Fellowship Discovery Platform

> **Find your next big opportunity with AI.** AI-OppHub connects Indian innovators with live hackathons, grants, and fellowships — powered by AWS Bedrock Claude AI, WhatsApp alerts, and real-time data from Devfolio.

🌐 **Live Demo:** [ai-opphub-next.vercel.app](https://ai-opphub-next.vercel.app)

---

## ✨ Features

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| 🔍 **Explore Opportunities** | Browse live, ongoing 2026 hackathons from Devfolio API |
| 🤖 **AI Pitch Grader** | Paste or upload your pitch — Claude AI scores it 0–100 with detailed feedback |
| 📱 **WhatsApp Alerts** | Get opportunity alerts & sync your account via Twilio WhatsApp |
| 💾 **Save & Apply** | Bookmark opportunities and track applications locally |
| 🎯 **AI Match Scores** | Every opportunity has a personalized AI match % |

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS |
| **AI Backend** | AWS Bedrock (Claude 3 Haiku) |
| **WhatsApp** | Twilio WhatsApp API (Sandbox) |
| **Live Data** | Devfolio Hackathon API |
| **Hosting** | Vercel |

